g.text: Use Case Scenario 1: Manager Creates Automated Workflow (Frontend Flow)
Scenario: Manager logs in, accesses Workspace, opens Workflow Builder,
drags and drops nodes, connects them, configures properties, and saves the workflow.
Display: Node Name, Description, Channel, Condition
End: Manager successfully created and saved the workflow.
Data is stored in DB and can be reopened anytime.
